      <text xml:space="preserve">{{Infobox disease
|  Name           = Charcot-Marie-Tooth disease
|  Image          = Charcot-marie-tooth foot.jpg
|  Caption        = The foot of a person with Charcot-Marie-Tooth. The lack of muscle, a high arch, and claw toes are signs of the genetic disease.
|  DiseasesDB     = 5815
|  DiseasesDB_mult= {{DiseasesDB2|2343}} 
