{{Infobox person
| image        = Drew Barrymore 2 by David Shankbone.jpg
| caption      = Drew Barrymore at the [[Tribeca Film Festival]], May 2007
| birth_name   = Drew Blyth Barrymore
| birth_date   = {{Birth date and age|mf=yes|1975|2|22}}&lt;ref name=&quot;Hello-Profile&quot; /&gt;
| birth_place  = [[Culver City, California]], [[United States|U.S.]]
